Class MergeRequest<T>

java.lang.Object
com.linecorp.centraldogma.client.MergeRequest<T>
public final class MergeRequest<T> extends Object
Prepares to send a CentralDogma.mergeFiles(String, String, Revision, MergeQuery) request to the Central Dogma repository.

  • Method Details

    • get

      public CompletableFuture<MergedEntry<T>> get()
      Retrieves the merged entry of the MergeQuery at the Revision.HEAD. Only JSON entry merge is currently supported. The JSON files are merged sequentially as specified in the MergeQuery.

      Note that only ObjectNode is recursively merged traversing the children. Other node types are simply replaced.

      Returns:
      the MergedEntry which contains the result of the merge

    • get

      public CompletableFuture<MergedEntry<T>> get(Revision revision)
      Retrieves the merged entry of the MergeQuery at the Revision. Only JSON entry merge is currently supported. The JSON files are merged sequentially as specified in the MergeQuery.

      Note that only ObjectNode is recursively merged traversing the children. Other node types are simply replaced.

      Returns:
      the MergedEntry which contains the result of the merge
